<figureCitation box="[159,255,1477,1503]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,250,1227,1251]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,385,1197]" captionTargetId="figure-104@5.[151,1436,380,1203]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. Mayawa bimaculata sp. nov., male holotype. A-B, lateral and dorsal habitus; C, head and anterior part of thorax, anterior view; D, base of abdomen, ventral view; E, genital capsule, lateral view; F, styles, connective, valve and subgenital plate, ventral view; G, aedeagus, posteroventral view; H, aedeagus, lateral view. I–M, female paratype: I, abdominal sternite VII; J, first valvula; K, detail of same; L, second valvulae; M, detail of same." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4556773" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4556773/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="580">Figure 3</figureCitation>
